v19

## Changes

* Adds support for the GitHub Actions runners `macos-11`, `macos-12`, `ubuntu-18.04` and `ubuntu-22.04`, in addition to the already supported runners `macos-10.15` and `ubuntu-20.04 / ubuntu-latest`. This fixes the long-standing issue https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/issues/7.

## Supported runners

* ubuntu-18.04
* ubuntu-20.04
* ubuntu-22.04
* macos-10.15
* macos-11
* macos-12
